<h3>Krabi Ao Nang &amp; Railay</h3>
<p>Well-known for its beaches and limestone mountains, Ao Nang is the main tourist destination in Krabi and has a wide range of hotels and amenities.</p>
</div>
<div class="des2"><a href="destinations/koh-lanta-islands.htm"><img src="images/destinations/koh-lanta-islands.jpg" title="Phang Nga Bay Private Yachts Charters" alt="Phang Nga Bay Private Yachts Charters" /></a>
<h3>Koh Lanta Islands</h3>
<p>Koh Lanta is actually a group of 52 islands that form the southernmost district of Krabi province. The two largest islands, Koh Lanta Yai and Koh Lanta Noi (Big Lanta and Little Lanta) are separated by a narrow strait which also includes the small island of Koh Klang. Fifteen of the islands in this group are included in the Koh Lanta National Marine Park.</p>
</div>
